details.name: Phantasm
details.description: Summons several phantasmal copies of the Chaos Knight from alternate dimensions. The phantasms deal 50/75/100% damage, but take 260% damage. Upgradeable by Aghanim's Scepter.\nDISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel
details.upgrade_description: Reduces incoming illusion damage to %incoming_damage_tooltip_scepter%%%, reduces cooldown to %cooldown_scepter% seconds and allows Phantasm to be cast on an allied hero. 1200 Cast Range
